        "description": "<p>Just a few months before the 2007 ICC Cricket World Cup, Rayad Emrit received his maiden international call-up when he was included in the West Indian squad to face India in their ODI series.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEmrit debuted for Trinidad in the 2003-04 season, and has since then been an important member of the side. An all-rounder who bowls medium pace, he has been in the scheme of things for Trinidad & Tobago in all forms. He was also part of the Stanford Superstars squad for the Twenty20 competition, but did not feature in the final eleven.</p>",
