        "description": "<p>Kedar Devdhar is a wicket-keeper batsman from Baroda and has represented the state team in domestic cricket. He has played for Baroda Cricket Association XI. His first-class debut came against Maharashtra in 2009 where his unbeaten 53 helped Baroda chase a target of 101 runs.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHe was signed by the Deccan Chargers in 2011 ahead of IPL’s season 4.</p>",
