        "description": "<p>Bhargav Bhatt is a slow left-arm bowler hailing from the state of Gujarat. He represents Baroda in first-class cricket. He made his first-class debut against Maharashtra in 2009.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHe was bought by the Kings XI Punjab ahead of the fourth IPL season. </p>",
