        "description": "<p>Javed Ahmadi is a right-handed batsman and bowls right-arm off break. He first represented the Afghanistan Under-19 side in the 2010 World Cup in New Zealand. He made his senior team ODI debut in July 2010 in the ICC World Cricket League Division One match against Scotland. Later that year, he went on to make his first-class debut against Kenya in the ICC Intercontinental Cup and scored a half-century on debut in the second innings.</p>",
