        "playerID": "61832",
        "birthPlace": "Ireland",
        "dob": "15/08/1991",
        "description": "<p>Left-handed Stuart Thompson made his first-class debut in 2012 against Afghanistan and was soon fast-tracked into Ireland’s T20I side ahead of the World Twenty20 in Sri Lanka.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe youngster was a revelation to the selectors when he scored a composed knock of 67 to help Ireland beat Uganda in the Under-19 World Cup Qualifying tournament. Stuart’s father, Nigel also played for Ireland.</p>",
