        "description": "<p>Ishank Jaggi is a right-handed batsman from the steel city, Jharkhand. He made his first-class debut in the year 2008 against Jammu and Kashmir and was a consistent run-getter in the Ranji Trophy for his state.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJaggi played for the Bangalore Royal Challengers in the 2010 edition of the IPL. He was then roped in by the Deccan Chargers for its 2011 season.</p>",
