        "description": "<p>Beuran Hendricks is a South African left-arm fast bowler who has represented his country in T20Is till now. Hendricks is known for his variations in delivery. He can swing the ball and at the same time has a very good deceptive slower ball which makes him a good death-bowler too. His domestic T20 performances have been very impressive and that's why he got a national call and made his T20I debut versus Australia in March 2014.</p>",
