        "description": "<p>A reliable and accurate fast bowler, he is known for his economy – in Tests he conceded just 2.81 runs per over, and 4.86 in the shorter game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA determined character, he has had a series of career-threatening stress fractures to his back but has overcome them to return fitter and stronger.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHis best bowling in Tests is 7-57 against Sri Lanka in 2003.</p>",
