        "description": "<p>Known as ‘Boeta’, which means ‘little brother’ in Afrikaans.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA lover of poetry, he is also an amateur astronomer and enjoys outdoor pursuits, particularly fishing.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHas batted at every position between 1 and 9, but has settled as an opening batsman.</p>",
