        "description": "<p>Hit a match-winning six against Kenya in the final of the 1997 ICC Trophy in Kuala Lumpur.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nScored a second-innings century in St Lucia to force a draw against West Indies in June 2004.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHas a double century in first-class cricket against Khulna Division during 2001-02 in Bangladesh’s National Cricket League.</p>",
