        "name": "Panagodage Don Ruchira Laksiri Perera",
        "playerID": "2354",
        "birthPlace": "Sri Lanka",
        "dob": "06/04/1977",
        "description": "<p>Took 3 for 55 on his ODI debut against England at Perth during the 1998-99 Carlton and United Series and his wickets all came in his first spell.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHad to wait seven years between his second and third ODI caps, January 1999 to January 2006.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHis List A one-day record includes an impressive strike rate of 29 balls per wicket and an average of 23.95.</p>",
