        "birthPlace": "Zimbabwe",
        "dob": "30/08/1984",
        "description": "<p>Tall, strong seam bowler from the Midlands province, who hits the deck hard with a high action.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHas improved his game through English club cricket and the Gloucestershire second XI.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMissed much of West Indies tour in 2006 with a broken hand.</p>",
