        "description": "<p>Called up to the Zimbabwe side in 2006 despite not having played local cricket since 2003-04.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHit two centuries in the warm-up matches on tour in West Indies in 2006, but made just 23 in six innings during the one-day series.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHas lost 16 kg since West Indies tour and continues to work on his fitness.</p>",
