        "description": "<p>A powerful hitter, especially against spinners and medium-pacers and a useful change bowler with off-breaks or slow seamers.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBorn in South Africa but grew up and lives in Bulawayo.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor Matabeleland against Manicaland in 2003/4 he scored 128 and 104 and hit 16 sixes in the match.</p>",
