        "dob": "07/08/1983",
        "description": "<p>Took five wickets in an innings in his ICC Intercontinental Cup debut in 2006. Scored his first ODI half-century against Ireland at the Pepsi ICC World Cricket League Division 1 in January 2007. Favourite player is Brian Lara. Enjoys hiking, watching movies and reading in his spare time. Picked up 3-56 against Zimbabwe in February 2009 and 3-59 against South Africa in October 2008.</p>",
