        "playerID": "3763",
        "birthPlace": "New Zealand",
        "dob": "26/05/1973",
        "description": "<p>Scored 119 runs at a strike-rate of 95.96 at ICC CWC Qualifier in South Africa in April this year. Played for Canterbury and Otago in his native New Zealand before moving to Netherlands. After conceding 82 runs on his ODI debut against Sri Lanka, he came back strongly to take 3-54 in his next game against the same opposition. Scored 104 against Ireland at Nairobi in 2007, his maiden ODI century. Scored 196 off 117 balls with 20 fours and 12 sixes in a European Championship match against Norway at Dublin in 2008.</p>",
