        "description": "<p>A talented young spinner, who can also contribute with the bat. Made his ODI debut against Sri Lanka, dismissing Sanath Jayasuriya and Kumar Sangakkara. Played in his side&rsquo;s win over Scotland during the ICC Cricket World Cup 2007.</p>",
