        "description": "<p>Has best ODI bowling figures of 3-23 against Bermuda at Rotterdam in 2007. Made his debut for Netherlands in an ICC Intercontinental Cup match against Bermuda at Amstelveen in 2007. His twin brother, Mark, played for Netherlands in ICC CWC 2007. Favourite cricketer is Andrew Symonds. Enjoys soccer and playing computer games.</p>",
