        "playerID": "4381",
        "birthPlace": "Bangladesh",
        "dob": "20/12/1993",
        "description": "<p>Saikat Ali, a talented all-rounder who admires Jacques Kallis for his all-round abilities, represented Bangladesh in the 2008 and 2010 Under-19 World Cups. He has got a first class century and 3 half century and has still a long way to go if he wants to be a part of the national side and stand out in international cricket.</p>",
