        "birthPlace": "India",
        "dob": "22/09/1986",
        "description": "<p>Representing the Bengal cricket team on the domestic one-day front, Debabrata Das is a right handed middle order batsman and a part time wicket keeper and has also plied his trade for India at the Under-19 level. A useful middle order batsman who is capable of big hits, he was part of the Kolkata squad in the inaugural Indian T20 League season in 2008. They re-signed him in 2012 for the fifth edition of in 2012 and will once again be a part of the team for the 2014 edition.</p>",
