        "description": "<p>Nayan Doshi is a left-arm spin bowler and son of former Indian Test player Dilip Doshi. Nayan was born and raised in England. However, he debuted in first-class cricket in India for Saurashtra in 2001-02. He also broke into the Surrey side in the year 2004 and played a major part in their National League and Twenty20 campaigns. He has also represented Buckinghamshire and Derbyshire.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHe was bought by the Royal Challengers Bangalore in the initial seasons of the IPL, but was later signed by the Rajasthan Royals in 2011.</p>",
