        "playerID": "4940",
        "birthPlace": "Sri Lanka",
        "dob": "20/07/1991",
        "description": "<p>Scored 207 runs at the ICC U19 Cricket World Cup 2010 Qualifier, including two half centuries. Compares his style of batting to Kumar Sangakkara. Made his ODI debut in July 2008 against Bermuda aged just 16. His father, Niron Gunasekera, made five first-class appearances in Sri Lanka. He is currently enrolled in a Business Management (BBA) course at the Scarborough Campus of the University of Toronto.</p>",
