        "birthPlace": "Kenya",
        "dob": "11/04/1990",
        "description": "<p>A highly promising batter, he is the son of David Waters. Hit 74 runs against South Africa in November 2008. Scored 75 runs in the ICC Intercontinental Cup match against Ireland in October 2008. Made his Surrey 2nd X1 debut in 2008, having performed brilliantly in schools cricket for Cranleigh School.</p>",
