        "dob": "20/04/1991",
        "description": "<p>Ankit Sharma is a left-handed batsman and also a left-arm bowler. He hails from Madhya Pradesh and has represented his state in first-class cricket. He also plays for India Revenue.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHe made his first-class debut against Kerala in 2009. In 2011, at the young age of 20, he was picked by the Hyderabad team for the fourth season of the Indian T20 League. In 2014, he was picked by the Rajasthan team at Rs. 10 lakhs for the seventh season.</p>",
