        "description": "<p>His favorite cricketing memory is Shahid Afridi’s century in 37 balls against Sri Lanka in Nairobi in 1996, and wants to emulate his idol in his skills.|His favourite film is “Mann” and likes listening to ‘Mera Mann’ from the same film.|He enjoys eating vegetarian food and wants to be a bowling coach when he grows up.|Took 3-18 against Qatar in the Asian Cricket Council (ACC) U15 Cup 2004-05 in April 2005.</p>",
