        "description": "<p>Alex Keath is a Victorian all-rounder who modeled himself around fellow teammate Andrew McDonald. At a young age he had to make a choice between the AFL and cricket and he chose the latter when he signed a full three-year contract with Victoria. He was part of Australia's Under-19 World Cup winning squad in 2012 but made his mark when he picked up 4 wickets for the Prime Ministers XI against West Indies.</p>",
