        "dob": "05/12/1983",
        "description": "<p>Ajit Chandila is an all-rounder from the state of Haryana. He is a right-hand batsman and a right-arm off break bowler. He was signed by the Delhi Daredevils ahead of the fourth IPL season in 2011, leading to his debut in the IPL.</p>",
