        "playerID": "11915",
        "birthPlace": "Bangladesh",
        "dob": "20/10/1986",
        "description": "<p>Fondly known to his teammates as 'Shiplu', Robiul Islam is right-arm medium pacer who made his first-class debut for the Khulna Division in 2005. He has also represented the Bangladeshi A team.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRobiul marked his international debut in a Test match against England in 2010, but was not picked for the next Test. He then made a comeback against Zimbabwe in their only Test in 2011.</p>",
