        "description": "<p>Hailing from Guyana, Christopher Barnwell is a right-handed batsman and right-arm medium pacer. He exhibited both skills in the domestic arena, taking regular wickets and contributing with the bat. His nagging lengths and clever change of pace made him Guyana’s most consistent seamer. Barnwell made his T20I debut in the 2011 home series against Pakistan. Two years later, he was bought by the Royal Challengers Bangalore for IPL season six.</p>",
