        "description": "<p>A slow left-arm orthodox bowler and a useful lower-order batsman, Garey Mathurin made his first-class debut for Windward Islands in 2007. He had a fantastic 2011 season, claiming 7 for 72 against England Lions and 5 for 86 when playing against Leeward Islands. His impressive performances led to his T20I call-up for the series against England in the same year.</p>",
