        "birthPlace": "Australia",
        "dob": "27/07/1989",
        "description": "<p>Cameron is a promising young right handed leggie from Queensland. With terrific bowling performances with the ball and decent contributions with the bat in First Class matches, he seems to have impressed the selectors at such young age. Plays for Queensland and Adelaide Strikers as an all rounder.</p>",
