        "description": "<p>He is the only player to have appeared in all 23 of Kenya`s matches in ICC CWC, scoring 724 runs at an average of 34.47. Has played in over 110 ODIs, with three ODI centuries and over 20 half centuries. Second in the all-time list of leading wicket-takers for his country. Short-listed for the inaugural ICC Associate ODI Player of the Year in 2007. Favourite cricketer is Sir Viv Richards.</p>",
