        "dob": "10/06/1978",
        "description": "<p>His first first-class wicket, for Derbyshire, was Steve Waugh, in May 1997. He moved down to Somerset three years later.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSmashed 28 off Matthew Hoggard in 2002, unknowingly in front of Duncan Fletcher, and in the same year was called up to the England squad.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAppointed Somerset captain in 2005.</p>",
