        "playerID": "3466",
        "birthPlace": "Holland",
        "dob": "21/06/1972",
        "description": "<p>Appointed Netherlands captain after ICC CWC 2007. Took the most dismissals at ICC CWC Qualifier in South Africa in April this year with 19 (ct 18, st 1). Made an ODI best score of 29 not out against Bermuda at Potchefstroom during the ICC CWC Qualifier in South Africa in April this year. Has taken the most dismissals for Netherlands in ODIs with 43 (ct 37, st 6). His idol is Jack Russell.</p>",
